data.description:
Come check out this fully 3- bedroom, 2-bathroom single family residential home. This home features beautiful vinyl plank floors, new paint and has been freshly painted inside. Conveniently located minutes away from major highways, making it for a quick and easy commute.
Make your appointment to see this beauty today!

Rental is responsible for lights and water. Last month rent is due at signing. There will be $150 pet fee. Rental application is $50.
